ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 22nd day of August, 2012, the “King’s Bench Application for Extraordinary Relief’ is DISMISSED, and the Prothonotary is directed to forward the filing to counsel of record. See Commonwealth v. Reid, 537 Pa. 167, 642 A.2d 453 (1994) (hybrid representation not permitted). The Prothonotary is directed to strike the names of the jurists from the caption.
